font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="background: rgb(255,255,255); padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; margin: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; padding-right: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">（</font>4）4段组晋升5段比例：&nbsp;各组实际参赛人数的15%</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="background: rgb(255,255,255); padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; margin: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; padding-right: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">五</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">、比赛时限：</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="background: rgb(255,255,255); padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; margin: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; padding-right: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; 