nt-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">各段位小组采用</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&ldquo;比较积分区分名次&rdquo;方法，积分高者名次列前。若积分相同，则比较对手分，对手分高者列前。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="background: rgb(255,255,255); padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; margin: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; padding-right: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、本次比赛</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">排名及</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; background: rgb(255,255,255); text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><font face="黑体">晋升名次不并列。遇有积分相同，对手分也相同，则依次比较违例次数、直胜、逐轮递减法（即采用去除选手第一轮对手积分后比较对手分，对手分高者列前；若仍无法区分名次，则依次去除第二轮、第三轮</font>&hellip;&hellip;对手分进行比较，直至能够区分名次为止）排出各组名次。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 黑体; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="bac