:4.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">11号13点至18：30白桦林赛场至太阳宫地铁直达</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18.0000pt;"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">注：需要乘坐直达车的选手请电话或短信</span><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">15910320307</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;">王老师</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">联系订时间，以便安排车次。</font> <font face="宋体">直达车收费标准为成人单程</font></span><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;">35元</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18.0000pt;"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">儿童（</font>1.2米以下）17元。白桦林景区内停车收费标准为每天五元，其它地方免费。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3．</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">活动要点：</font>1白</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">桦林森林公园旅游</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">：五龙潭、冰川三条旅游观光带总面积为</font>4500公顷，植物种类有677种，动物共计300多种，是一个生物多样性的王国。国内面积最大的白桦林、紫桦林(2500公顷);有北京最大面积的高山杜鹃、落叶松林、原始次生橡