ound-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本次比赛北京地区选手使用北京棋院最新推出围棋段位证书与中国棋院的段位证书一同配套发放，所有证书信息将录入</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此次比赛报名网站</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">系统，便于棋手日后网上报名参赛及身份核验。晋升时需交</span>1寸照片两张并上报身份证号。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">九</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、特别提示</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（一）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">参赛者需网上报名，不接受任何形式的电话和现场报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（二）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">参赛选手须持网报打印确认审核通过的报名表。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; box-si