(61, 8, '“千家店百里山水画廊杯”业余围棋段位赛补充规定', '<p>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 18pt; text-align: center;">2017年北京市延庆区&ldquo;千家店百里山水画廊杯&rdquo;业余围棋段位赛补充规定</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:32.0000pt;"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:32.0000pt;"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">参加</font>&ldquo;延庆杯&rdquo;的棋手，请查阅补充规定后的各等级分组名单，</span><u><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">于</font>26号下午14:00-17:00在千家店镇长寿岭围棋村村口大榆树下领取参赛证</span></u><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">，比赛凭证入场，请大家提前做好准备。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:32.0000pt;"><u><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">联系电话：</font>13381119066曹老师</span></u><u><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">一．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">比赛时间、地点：</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2017年7月27日上午8:30开赛，上午3轮，下午1:30开赛，下午4轮。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7月28日上午8:30开赛，2轮。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">地址：北京市延庆区千家店学校</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">二．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">比赛办法</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、比赛采用中国围棋协会审定的最新竞赛规则(2002年版)</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、赛制：各组均采用9轮积分编排。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、各组按比例晋升高一级段位（以实际参赛人数为准）。具体比例为：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;1级组35% &nbsp;1段组30% &nbsp;&nbsp;2段组25% &nbsp;&nbsp;3段组20% &nbsp;&nbsp;4段组15%</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4、每轮比赛的先后手，均由电脑编排确定。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">5、黑方先行，黑贴3又3/4子（7目半）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">三．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">比赛时限：</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、1级组,1段组和2段组比赛双方共用1小时，比赛开始40分钟后由裁判员视棋局进程加钟计时，每方各10分钟包干，超时判负。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、3段组和4段组比赛每方30分钟包干，超时判负。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、如比赛时有故意搅局者，裁判组有权视情况予以相应判罚。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4、每轮比赛，自裁判长宣布比赛开始，逾15分钟未能到达赛场者，按弃权论处，此轮判负。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">5、棋手无故未到赛场，视为退赛，自下轮起不再进行编排。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">四．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">名次区分：</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">本次比赛采用</font>&ldquo;比较积分区分名次&rdquo;方法，积分高者名次列前，若积分相同，则比较对手分，对手分高者名次列前。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">本次比赛名次不并列。若积分相同，对手分也相同，则依次比较违例次数，直胜，逐轮递减法（即采用去除选手第一轮对手积分后比较对手分，对手分高者名次列前。若仍无法区分名次，则依次去除第二轮，第三轮</font>&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;对手分进行比较，直至能够区分名次为止。）排出各组名次。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">五．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">关于申诉：</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="仿宋_GB2312">棋手对裁判员的裁决有异议，必须在当轮比赛结束后半个小时内以书面形式向裁判长提出申诉，并交纳</font>500元申诉费，胜诉后退还。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">六．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">赛场纪律：</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、尊重对手，遵守规则，服从裁判。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、棋局结束后，胜方持双方台签主动至计分台签字计分，收好棋子后退场，不得滞留在赛场内围观，拆棋或复盘。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">保持赛场内安静，不得大声喧哗，进入赛场要关闭手机，赛场内禁止吸烟。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">七．</span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">未尽事宜，另行通知。</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;"><b><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1500883483, '', 0, 'http://', ''),
