9px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">二、承办单位：中国音乐学院附属北京实验学校</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">三、支持单位：北京棋院</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">四、比赛时间：</span>2016年11月5-6</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">日</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">五、比赛地点：中国音乐学院附属北京实验学校（朝阳区仰山路</span>9号）</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">六、参赛资格</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体">参赛选手需持现有相应等级的北京棋院登记颁发的有效段位证书方可报名参赛。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">七、竞赛办法：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(一)本次比赛采用中国棋院2002年颁布的《中国围棋规则》</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(二)赛制：电脑积分编排</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(三)竞赛分组：1段组（持业余1段证书)，2段组（持业余2段证书），3段组(持业余3段证书），4段组（持业余4段证书）。本次比赛不允许跨级别报名，一经查实取消比赛资格，所有参赛运动员报名及入场时需提交相应段位证书备查。</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(四)本次比赛男女不分组</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)"><span style="font-family: 宋体">八、报名办法</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(一)报名方式：网上报名</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(二)报名时间：网上报名从10月21日9时起至10月25日17时截止</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(三)报名方法：网上报名请登录北京棋院培训中心（www.leqiworld.com），点击弈&bull;会员板块，下拉选择活动缴费栏目，注册成功后，点击左侧报考列表报名。过程中需提交相应等级证明材料并缴费，缴费成功等待审核，审核状态显示成功后再点击右上角返回我的报名，打印参赛证明。</span></p>\r\n<p style="background: rgb(255,255,255); white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/1.5em ''microsoft yahei'', Tahoma, Arial; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47,47,47)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(四)本次比赛报名电脑自动优先匹配审核数据库已有信息，各位参赛选手先行查询本身信息是否已经在数据库备案，未查询到备案的选手可于10月19日10点起进行网上信息填写，提前接受审核。</span></p>', 'images/201702/thumb_img/107_thumb_G_1488271107170.jpg', 'images/201702/goods_img/107_G_1488271107929.jpg', 'images/201702/source_img/107_G_1488271107406.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 2, 1488271107, 100, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1488603170, 0, '', -1, -1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', '', '0.00', '0.00', '', '', 0, NULL),
